.help polypars May88 noao.digiphot.apphot
.ih
NAME
polypars -- edit the polyphot photometry parameters
.ih
USAGE
polypars
.ih
PARAMETERS
.ls zmag = 26.00
The zero point offset for the magnitude scale.
.le
.ls mkpolygon = no
Draw the polygons on the screen.
.le
.ih
DESCRIPTION
The zero point of the magnitude scale is determined by \fIzmag\fR.
If the \fImkpolygon\fR switch enabled polygons are marked on the screen.
.ih
EXAMPLES

1. List the polyphot photometry parameters.

.nf
	ap> lpar polypars
.fi

2. Edit the polyphot photometry parameters.

.nf
	ap> polypars
.fi

.ih
TIME REQUIREMENTS
.ih
BUGS
.ih
SEE ALSO
polyphot
.endhelp
